sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as DemoHttpServer
    participant F as Fridge
    participant OP as OrderProcessor (Child)
    participant GS as GroceryStore (gRPC Service)

    Note over UI, GS: User orders 2x Milk
    UI->>F: Ask: OrderProduct(product, quantity, replyTo)
    
    alt Capacity Exceeded (Weight or Volume)
        F-->>UI: OrderResponse(success=false, error_reason)
    else Capacity OK
        F->>OP: Spawn Child Actor
        F-->>UI: OrderResponse(success=true, "Order placed")
        
        Note over OP, GS: Asynchronous gRPC Call
        OP->>GS: processOrder(OrderRequest)
        GS-->>OP: OrderReceipt (CompletionStage)
        
        OP->>F: Tell: OrderCompleted(receipt)
        Note over OP: Child Actor Stops (stopped)
        
        F->>F: Update Inventory & History
        F->>F: notifySubscribers() (SSE Update)
    end
